title: AUD/USD Responds Well to Slope and Fibonacci Combination
text:
Wed, Jul 22, 2015, 6:37 AM AEST - Australia Markets open in 3 hrs 23 mins AUD/USD Responds Well to Slope and Fibonacci Combination By Jamie Saettele, CMT | DailyFX – 2 hours 56 minutes ago Recommend Automate trades with Mirror Trader and see ideas on other USD crosses -“June’s AUDUSD range (3.4%) was the smallest monthly range since October (3.05%). In fact, the intermonth plots of price action for June and October are virtually identical. Both time series form 3 wave corrective (A-B-C) patterns.” -“Focus remains lower towards .7100/50 but there is support down here from Fibonacci (127.2% extension of the April-May rally).” The line that extends off of the February and March lows also provided support. A close above downtrend resistance (near .7500) is needed in order to indicate a larger reversal is underway.
